<HEAD>LaserPhoto CX4</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By DAVID ROCKS</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>HIGHLAND PARK, Ill. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
